AmfController
=============

Adds a set of generic CRUD actions to controller

Example
=======

class InvoicesController < ApplicationController
 amf_controller
end


class InvoicesController < ApplicationController
 amf_controller :model => Report
end

class InvoicesController < ApplicationController
 amf_controller :actions => [:read, :update]
end


